<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <title>Definir nova senha — Portal Cientifico</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Archivo:wght@700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
    body{font-family:'IBM Plex Sans',system-ui,sans-serif;background:#0C231B;min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:20px}
    .wrap{width:100%;max-width:400px}
    .card{background:#fff;padding:32px}
    .card-icon{width:48px;height:48px;background:#f0fdf4;border:2px solid #bbf7d0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px}
    .card h2{font-size:17px;font-weight:700;color:#0C231B;margin-bottom:6px}
    .card p{font-size:13px;color:#6B7A72;margin-bottom:24px;line-height:1.5}
    .form-group{margin-bottom:16px}
    .form-group label{display:block;font-size:11.5px;font-weight:600;color:#4A5568;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.7px;margin-bottom:6px}
    .form-group input{width:100%;padding:10px 13px;border:1.5px solid #DDE3DF;background:#F8FAF9;color:#0C231B;font-size:14px;font-family:inherit;border-radius:0;outline:none}
    .form-group input:focus{border-color:#0F6E56;background:#fff}
    .btn{width:100%;padding:11px;background:#0F6E56;color:#fff;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit}
    .btn:hover{background:#0a5240}
    .alert-err{padding:10px 14px;background:#fef2f2;border:1px solid #fecaca;color:#b91c1c;font-size:13px;margin-bottom:16px}
    .brand{text-align:center;margin-bottom:28px;color:#5E7A6D;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">
  <div class="brand">Portal Cientifico</div>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-icon">
      <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#15803d" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg>
    </div>
    <h2>Defina sua senha</h2>
    <p>Este e seu primeiro acesso. Por seguranca, crie uma senha pessoal para continuar.</p>
    <%if(erro&&erro.length){%><div class="alert-err"><%=erro[0]%></div><%}%>
    <form method="POST" action="<%=baseUrl%>/trocar-senha">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label>Nova senha</label>
        <input type="password" name="nova_senha" required minlength="6" placeholder="Minimo 6 caracteres">
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label>Confirmar senha</label>
        <input type="password" name="confirmar_senha" required minlength="6" placeholder="Repita a senha">
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn">Salvar e entrar</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>
</body></html>
